      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIAMOND LUCY (8) staged a form reversal last start to get the money at massive odds in a Class 1 over 1200m at Townsville. Drops 3kgs on that run so although her strike rate is not enviable another big run looks on the cards. ELLIE'S DREAM (1) settled close to the pace then boxed on well for second over 1200m at Laura last time out. In the money nine times from 14 runs here at this trip. Sound each-way prospects again. VOUCHERS (3) is back after an 18-week spell. Sure to improve on whatever he does today but he does like racing here so a brighter first-up run than usual will not surprise. FLOURISH (7) is back after a three-month absence. Goes Vell at this circuit and from gate one with a light weight comes right under notice. LA MANO (6) has been freshened up since a disappointing run at Atherton on 13 June. Each-way hope if anywhere near her best.",
